com.laughingmasq.pong.game

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.laughingmasq.pong.game.Entity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Ball, Pad

    public abstract class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
    Super class for all entities (especially movable) in the game. All entities should be using this class as a base.
    Author:
    schme
